<task id="task_A2819A92942D400880A62FFD86FE952B">
  <title>Place an Mbox Around a Table</title>
  <shortdesc>It is often useful to place an mbox around a table. 
  </shortdesc>
  <prolog>
    <metadata>
      <othermeta name="solution" content="Target" />
      <othermeta name="topic" content="Advanced" />
    </metadata>
  </prolog>
  <taskbody>
    <steps id="steps_B990A96A402545CBA5F910DD42733554">
      <step id="step_B6B8548D2F6A43D4B01E5DA3A3B5E23E">
        <cmd> Make sure the page includes a reference to 
			 <filepath>mbox.js</filepath> in the header. 
		  </cmd>
      </step>
      <step id="step_09BFAB90DCA440B2ABA0393E7822735A">
        <cmd>Insert mbox default function just before the table's tags. 
		  </cmd>
      </step>
      <step id="step_C0A4262A1D1943A8B840ACF1B059C208">
        <cmd> Immediately follow the default content close with the 
			 <codeph>mboxCreate</codeph> function. 
		  </cmd>
        <stepresult>
          <p>Give the mbox a unique name which makes sense for your campaign
				strategy and company procedures. In the example below, the mbox is named
				myMbox. 
			 </p>
          <p>
            <b>Important:</b>
          </p>
          <p>
            <ul id="ul_F4A23D7E894E45D19B9DCD075D48EC1F">
              <li id="li_9119488B79774D4F92D69D5789D1B5E7"> Ensure any tags left 
				  <b>open before</b> the mbox scripts are 
				  <b>closed after</b> the mbox scripts. 
				</li>
              <li id="li_2B5C8462F9AD437F9EB54DECF820F4A2"> Do not wrap rows.
				  Wrap only entire table or a single cell. 
				</li>
            </ul>
          </p>
          <p>Example of mbox around a table: 
			 </p>
          <p>
            <table id="table_87A6E0A2FAAA427BB8DF2D96B8BA87D9">
              <tgroup cols="2">
                <colspec colnum="1" colname="col1" colwidth="*" />
                <colspec colnum="2" colname="col2" colwidth="*" />
                <thead>
                  <row>
                    <entry colname="col1">Before 
						</entry>
                    <entry colname="col2">After 
						</entry>
                  </row>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
                  <row>
                    <entry colname="col1">
                      <p>
                        <codeblock outputclass="syntax html">&lt;head&gt;

&lt;/head&gt;

&lt;body&gt;

&lt;center&gt;

&lt;table bordercolor="red" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" width="560" align="left" border="0"&gt;
&lt;tbody&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td align="left" width="12"&gt;&lt;/td&gt;

&lt;td align="left" width="475"&gt;
....
&lt;/table&gt;
&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;/tbody&gt;&lt;/table&gt;
&lt;/center&gt;</codeblock>
                      </p>
                    </entry>
                    <entry colname="col2">
                      <p>
                        <codeblock outputclass="syntax html" scale="90">&lt;head&gt;
&lt;script src="/myfolder/mbox.js" type="text/javascript"&gt;​​&lt;/script&gt;

&lt;/head&gt;

&lt;body&gt;

&lt;center&gt;

&lt;div class="mboxDefault"&gt;

&lt;table bordercolor="red"
cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" width="560" align="left" border="0"&gt;
&lt;tbody&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td align="left" width="12"&gt;&lt;/td&gt;

&lt;td align="left" width="475"&gt;
....
&lt;/table&gt;
&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;/tbody&gt;&lt;/table&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;script type="text/javascript"&gt;
mboxCreate('myMbox');
&lt;/script&gt;
&lt;/center&gt; </codeblock>
                      </p>
                    </entry>
                  </row>
                </tbody>
              </tgroup>
            </table>
          </p>
        </stepresult>
      </step>
      <step id="step_91320B85616247DAAA13B38514EAE6A3">
        <cmd>
          <xref href="t_Validating_an_Mbox.xml#task_4BB8E090CBBF4C56A39BB63BF1ADB964" type="task" format="dita" scope="local">Validate the mbox</xref>. 
		  </cmd>
      </step>
    </steps>
